	tristate "SERVERWORKS OSB4/CSB5/CSB6/HT1000 PATA support"
	depends on PCI
	help
	  This option enables support for the Serverworks OSB4/CSB5/CSB6 and
	  HT1000 PATA controllers, via the new ATA layer.

	  If unsure, say N.

